<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8"?>
<Subtitle>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>1</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>16947</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>24545</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>很久很久以前，有一座山，山顶上有块石头。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>2</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>24546</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>30960</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>天地日月每天都对这块石头施展着法术。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>3</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>30961</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>36030</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>有一天，这块石头裂开了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>4</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>36031</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>40468</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>一只猴子躺在石头里。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>5</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>40469</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>46935</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>猴子站起身来舒展着身体。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>6</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>46936</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>54316</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>突然，猴子的双眼射出了强光。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>7</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>54317</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>60795</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>不一会儿，这道光就照到了天庭的凌霄宝殿。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>8</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>60796</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>65562</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>天庭的最高统治者玉帝坐起身来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>9</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>65563</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>71196</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他扭头看着站在自己身边的一个天将。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>10</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>71197</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>75593</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“去看看哪里来的光。”玉帝说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>11</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>75594</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>79562</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“遵命，陛下。”天将回答。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>12</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>79563</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>83125</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>天将快速走出了凌霄宝殿。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>13</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>83126</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>92517</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他一路冲出了南天门，向下界看去，结果看到了那只猴子。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>14</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>92518</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>97893</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>那道光不见了，但这位天将的眼睛有法力。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>15</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>97894</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>102380</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他可以看到之前发生的一切。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>16</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>102381</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>105128</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“有意思。”天将说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>17</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>105129</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>113254</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“怎么了？”天将回到天宫时，玉帝问道。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>18</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>113255</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>116611</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“那光是从哪里来的？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>19</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>116612</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>120825</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“是一只猴子弄出来的。”天将说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>20</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>120826</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>124152</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“猴子？”玉帝问。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>21</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>124153</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>126961</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“是的。”天将回答道，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>22</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>126962</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>129681</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“他在人间的花果山上。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>23</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>129682</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>132167</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>那山上有块石头。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>24</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>132168</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>136921</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>那猴子就是从石头里蹦出来的。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>25</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>136922</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>142845</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>那道光是从猴子的眼睛里发出来的。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>26</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>142846</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>148275</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>玉帝想了一会儿，然后耸耸肩。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>27</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>148276</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>151788</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“那我就觉得不奇怪了。”他说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>28</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>151789</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>157797</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“天地合力之时，总有奇妙的事情发生。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>29</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>167268</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>177437</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>日子一天天过去，这只猴子学会了走、跑和爬。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>30</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>177438</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>184525</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他喝的是小溪里的水，吃的是草和树叶。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>31</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>184526</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>194299</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他摘果子，在山洞和山顶探险。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>32</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>194300</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>198179</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他成了其他所有猴子的朋友。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>33</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>198180</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>203639</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>到了晚上，他就在一个悬崖下睡觉。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>34</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>203640</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>212026</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>有一天早上，天气非常热，所有的猴子都在树荫里玩耍。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>35</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>212027</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>215912</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“今天太热了！”有只猴子叫道，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>36</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>215913</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>218249</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我们去小溪里玩儿吧！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>37</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>218250</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>222161</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“好主意！”另一只猴子回答道。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>38</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>222162</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>225766</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>一群猴子跑到了小溪边。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>39</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>225767</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>230831</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>水流冲击着石头，激起了朵朵水花。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>40</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>230832</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>234961</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>猴子们跳进了清凉的溪水里。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>41</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>234962</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>239106</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>所有猴子都在水里玩耍。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>42</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>239107</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>244246</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>过了一会儿，有只猴子挠了挠脑袋。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>43</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>244247</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>247857</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我们都喜欢这条小溪。”她说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>44</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>247858</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>250590</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我们喝小溪的水。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>45</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>250591</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>252513</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>我们在溪里游泳。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>46</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>252514</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>255690</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>我们知道它一路流到海里去，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>47</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>255691</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>260907</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>但有谁知道这条小溪的源头在哪里吗？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>48</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>260908</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>267959</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>猴子们你看看我，我看看你，都摇头。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>49</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>267960</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>273159</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我们今天也没什么事情做。”那只猴子继续说道，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>50</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>273160</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>278107</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“不如我们沿着小溪走，去找找它的源头？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>51</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>278108</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>282233</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“听上去挺有趣的。”另一只猴子说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>52</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>282234</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>286638</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“那我们走吧！”第三只猴子说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>53</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>286639</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>290122</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>猴子们都从水里跳了出来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>54</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>290123</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>296062</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他们沿着小溪一路走，从这棵树荡到那棵树上。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>55</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>296063</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>300844</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他们跳过一块块岩石，向山上爬去。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>56</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>300845</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>308042</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他们越爬越高，最后在一处巨大的瀑布前停住了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>57</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>308043</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>316666</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>空气里有很多水雾，水流下来，发出巨大的声音。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>58</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>316667</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>322518</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我想知道那瀑布后面是什么。”有只猴子说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>59</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>322519</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>326334</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我也想知道。”另一只猴子说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>60</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>326335</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>329539</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“但没人能穿过瀑布啊。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>61</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>329540</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>334423</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“只要谁可以穿过瀑布再活着回来，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>62</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>334424</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>338900</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>我们就封他为王。”一只长臂猿说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>63</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>338908</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>341846</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“有人敢去试试吗？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>64</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>341847</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>349494</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>猴子们你看看我，我看看你，都摇着头。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>65</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>349495</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>353777</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我不敢试。”一只高高的猴子说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>66</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>353778</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>359131</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我也不敢。”一只矮猴子说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>67</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>359132</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>362363</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>有人喊道：“我来！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>68</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>362364</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>367941</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>猴子们纷纷给那个说话的猴子让出道来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>69</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>367942</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>372243</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>是那只石头里蹦出来的猴子。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>70</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>372244</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>375928</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你确定要试试吗？”长臂猿问，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>71</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>375929</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>379253</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“这看上去挺危险的。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>72</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>379254</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>381489</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>石猴笑了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>73</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>381490</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>383172</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我什么都不怕！</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>74</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>383173</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>387027</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>我回来的时候，就是你们的大王啦！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>75</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>387028</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>393857</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>石猴做了个深呼吸，跳进了瀑布里。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
</Subtitle>